    {
      "id": "7973e4d5-36cd-41ba-ad0b-498ba761b441",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "# Example 2: Print all permutations of {1, 2, … n}\n\nExample: n = 3\n{1, 2, 3}\n{1, 3, 2}\n{2, 3, 1}\n{2, 1, 3}\n{3, 1, 2}\n{3, 2, 1}",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "7973e4d5-36cd-41ba-ad0b-498ba761b441"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3d2db600-c7fe-4b13-9de4-a116d66305a5",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "import java.util.Arrays;\r\n\r\n// 1. Hàm đệ quy\r\nvoid print_all_permutations(int n, int[] incomplete_str, boolean[] used, int pos) {\r\n    if (pos == n) {\r\n        System.out.println(Arrays.toString(incomplete_str));\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {\r\n        if (used[i] == false){\r\n            incomplete_str[pos] = i;\r\n            used[i] = true;\r\n            print_all_permutations(n, incomplete_str, used, pos + 1);\r\n            used[i] = false;\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 2. Hàm gọi\r\nvoid print_all_permu(int n) {\r\n    boolean[] used = new boolean[n+1];\r\n    int[] arr = new int[n];\r\n    // Bắt đầu từ 0\r\n    print_all_permutations(n, arr,used, 0);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 3. LỆNH CHẠY (Gõ dòng này thì nó mới in ra!)\r\nprint_all_permu(4);",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "java",
        "id": "3d2db600-c7fe-4b13-9de4-a116d66305a5",
        "executionSummary": {
          "executionOrder": 57,
          "success": true
        }
      },
